# React and TSX Conventions

- Follow hooks rules strictly: no conditional hook calls and no hook calls inside JSX conditions.
- Keep components focused; move side-effect-heavy logic to hooks or services.
- Prefer typed props and state over `any`.
- Preserve router guard patterns in `ProtectedRoute` and `Root`.
- Add brief comments only when logic is non-obvious.
